e__thumbnail__wrapper flex-no-shrink m-r-3-xs"><amp-img layout="responsive" src="https://video-images.vice.com/articles/5ac673591eaf4d0006ba6df0/lede/1522956158127-Deafheaven-pg2.jpeg?crop=0.295xw%3A0.2086xh%3B0.3505xw%2C0.7098xh&amp;resize=1250%3A*" height="1" width="1"></amp-img></div><div class="related__article__content col-12-xs"><div class="m-b-1-xs"><div class="canonical__topic hed-xs"><span>Comics</span></div></div><div class="related__article__title hed-m">&#x27;Enlightened Metalheads,&#x27; Today&#x27;s Comic by Pedro D&#x27;Apremont&#x27;s</div></div></a><a class="related__article dsp-flex-xs p-t-3-xs p-b-3-xs col-12-xs" title="Scott Pruitt Has Already Won" href="/en_us/article/ywxnqk/scott-pruitt-has-already-won"><div class="related__article__thumbnail__wrapper flex-no-shrink m-r-3-xs"><amp-img layout="responsive" src="https://video-images.vice.com/articles/5ac643787a492c0008d118f1/lede/1522955886149-Pruitt-Coal.jpeg?crop=0.4679xw%3A0.8941xh%3B0.5321xw%2C0xh&amp;resize=1250%3A*" height="1" width="1"></amp-img></div><div class="related__article__content col-12-xs"><div class="m-b-1-xs"><div class="canonical__topic hed-xs"><span>Scott Pruitt</span></div></div><div class="related__article__title hed-m">Scott Pruitt Has Already Won</div></div></a></div></div></div><a href="/" class="link-button link-button--branded text-center-xs dsp-block-xs m-b-4-xs m-b-6-m p-4-xs"><div class="latest-button__text">More from vice</div></a></div></div></div></article></div></div></div><div class="vice__footer grd p-l-4-xs p-r-4-xs p-t-6-xs p-b-6-xs p-t-7-m p-b-7-m p-l-6-m p-r-6-m p-l-7-xl p-r-7-xl"><div class="dsp-flex-xs flex-wrap site-width m-l-aut-xs m-r-aut-xs"><div class="col-12-xs text-center-xs"><amp-img class="site__logo m-b-4-xs m-b-5-m" src="https://vice-web-statics-cdn.vice.com/logos/vice_logo_white.svg" height="28" width="90" alt="footer logo"></amp-img></div><div class="vice__footer__copyright grd-col col-12-xs text-center-xs">© 2018 VICE Media LLC</div></div></